==Favoriting avatars==
Users can favorite avatars to save them for later. Favorited avatars will appear in the "favorites" row on the avatar page. Until 2019 only 3 favorite slots were available. Later to have 1 (3 with VRC+) favorite lists with 25 slots each. Today 3 lists, each can hold up to 50 avatars. With an active [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat+|VRC+ subscription]], you can access 5 additional avatar favorite lists.